full_text: I literally fucking hate jobs, I'm always saying I fucking hate jobs and hate working, and if I hadn't started this new job that I don't even fucking like, then I wouldn't have gotten fucking COVID I'm literally so fucking mad!!!!

People told me that they knew they had COVID bc they woke up feeling fucked up and not right on the first day, which happened to me, but no one warned me that it just makes you feel... weird and fucked up... it's hard to explain. Feels like a really, really bad hangover
